			<p class="question">Why did The Captain choose to feature you at Provo Yacht Club Part Deux?</p>
			<p class="answer">Our goal is not to play the "same ole thang." We play familiar music while also introducing new music.</p>

			<p class="question">What can people expect from your featured set at Part Deux?</p>
			<p class="answer">Our music selection will range from House to Disco to Funk and Hip-Hop.</p>

			<p class="question">What is your current outlook on dance music and where do you see it going?</p>
			<p class="answer">Dance music is different everwhere. It;s hard to pinpoint where dance will be or where we'd hope it to be but we think it would be important for people to find something they like and roll with it.</p>

			<p class="question">Don't miss House of Melk at Provo Yacht Club Part Deux. 9:00PM, Friday, January 30, 2015.</p>

